data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Perfect blend of elegance and comfort in this stunning 3-bedroom, 2 bathroom house, nestled in a pleasant neighborhood. With a new roof, HVAC system, garage door opener, water softener, and a tankless water heater, this home offers the epitome of modern living. As you enter this you'll be greeted by a spacious living room adorned with a vaulted ceiling, creating an open and airy atmosphere. Hardwood, tile, and vinyl floors that seamlessly flow throughout the entire home. The remodeled master bathroom is a sanctuary of relaxation, featuring modern fixtures. The kitchen is a chef's delight, with granite countertops providing both beauty and functionality. It's equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and ample cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze. The charm extends to the exterior, where you'll find a large back yard. Built-in tornado shelter for added safety.
